          <p><em>Trametes versicolor</em> — <strong>Gut Health & Immune Support.</strong> Contains some of the highest beta-glucan concentrations among medicinal mushrooms (PSP and PSK). Acts as a prebiotic while activating NK cells and T-cells. Over 400 clinical studies, the most evidence-backed species for immune modulation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-ico">CH</div>
          <h3>Chaga</h3>
          <p><em>Inonotus obliquus</em> — <strong>Antioxidant Protection.</strong> One of the highest ORAC scores of any natural food — 30x that of blueberries. Melanin and betulinic acid provide potent antioxidant and anti-inflammatory effects. Supports healthy aging, liver health, and blood sugar metabolism at the cellular level.</p>
