          <p><em>Grifola frondosa</em> — <strong>Blood Sugar & Immune Balance.</strong> Contains the unique D-fraction polysaccharide, shown to enhance NK cell activity and support healthy blood glucose metabolism. A 2015 study in <em>Journal of Medicinal Food</em> found maitake extract improved insulin sensitivity in overweight adults. Increasingly included in multi-mushroom gummy blends.</p>
