        <h3>How We Tested These Mushroom Gummies</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Purchase Verification:</strong> We bought every product with our own money from authorized retailers. No free samples, no sponsored placements, no brand partnerships influenced our rankings.</li>
          <li><strong>Ingredient Audit:</strong> We verified each product's supplement facts panel against manufacturer claims. We checked for fruiting body vs. mycelium sourcing, beta-glucan content disclosures, third-party testing certifications, and the presence of grain-based fillers.</li>
          <li><strong>Four-Week Trial:</strong> Each product was used daily for a minimum of four weeks by our testing team. We tracked subjective measures of focus, energy, sleep quality, and overall well-being using standardized daily logs.</li>
          <li><strong>Taste and Texture Evaluation:</strong> Gummies must be palatable for consistent daily use. We scored each product on flavor accuracy, sweetness balance, chewability, and aftertaste on a 1-to-10 scale.</li>
          <li><strong>Value Calculation:</strong> We calculated the true cost per serving, factored in dose adequacy relative to clinical research standards, and assessed whether the price-to-potency ratio justified the investment.</li>
          <li><strong>Literature Cross-Reference:</strong> We compared each product's formulation against published clinical research on PubMed to evaluate whether the included species and doses have meaningful scientific support.</li>
